content: Well this is not a thing that I have known to happen before. It does sound like a sad thing for the baby. But she is being called 'reincarnation of Hindu goddess'. If the family is happy then we can not think it bad. And the doctors say she is healthy and nothing wrong medically. https://nypost.com/2023/09/19/baby-with-26-fingers-and-toes-called-reincarnation-of-hindu-goddess/
